Shopify Commerece App Development:
- Built a shopify app that enables users to create QR codes for certain products and track the number of scans for each QR code. QR codes can include certain discounts, and can link to either the online store product page or directly to checkout with the product added to the cart.

The QR code app addresses a real-world merchant need and integrates seamlessly with the Shopify admin user interface. Users can create, view, edit, and delete QR codes using the app.

